General Conditions
AIR TRANSPORTATION. Comfort Class by Icelandic
Airlines only. Individual air fares based on 14- to 21-day

ACCOMMODATIONS. A twin-bedded room with
pri-
vate bath will be provided at a first class hotel for night of
arrival in Luxembourg.
MEALS. Breakfast, lunch and dinner will be provided
during above stay at Luxembourg hotel.
NOT INCLUDED. Accommodations, meals other than
stated above, beverages, porter tips,
airport taxes, laundry
and all other items of a personal nature are not included
in the price of the tour.
DOCUMENTS. A valid passport,
a smallpox certificate
and an International driver's license are all the documents
required of a U.S. citizen.
INSURANCE. Liability insurance
regarding the
car
rental is included in tour price. Full collision protection is
available on request.
RESTRICTIONS.
Automobiles can not be rented to
persons under 21 years of age.
MILEAGE CHARGE. Volkswagen 4¢, Opel 6¢, Merce-
des 8¢ per kilometer.
Reservations for Group Tours
Group tour departures (and prices) are subject to special
CAB regulations requiring that IAL have a minimum of
15 persons booked in each group. If for some reason this
number of participants have not been assembled, it may
become necessary to change the departure date.
All par-
ticipants will be advised of this at least 30 days prior to
departure.
A deposit of $70.00 is required at time of booking. Full
payment due at least 30 days before departure.
